Package it.polimi.ingsw.utils

Enum Action

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Action>
it.polimi.ingsw.utils.Action
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Action>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Action
extends java.lang.Enum<Action>
implements java.io.Serializable
This enum is an element that each PlayerAction and Pack must have. It specify what kind of action has ben made or what kind or information the server needs in order to let the game routine run properly.
